longBusinessSummary: Harvest Gold Corporation, an exploration stage company, engages in the acquisition, exploration, and development of natural resource properties. It explores for copper-gold porphyry projects. The company's flagship project is the Emerson property that covers an area of approximately 56 square kilometers located in the interior plateau of British Columbia. Harvest Gold Corporation was founded in 2005 and is headquartered in Vancouver, Canada.
